                    "company": "FMO - Dutch entrepreneurial development bank",
                    "description": "As Senior Legal Counsel a FMO, I play a leading role within the Legal Team of more than 30 professionals, handling complex transactions in frontier markets and providing internal training and knowledge leadership to the team. In my additional role of Legal Coordinator for the Agriculture, Food and Water (AFW) Department, I am responsible for strengthening interdepartmental relations, managing transactional workflow and providing a primary point of AFW subject matter knowledge.\n\nOn the transaction level and in my primary area of expertise, I advise deal teams on numerous high value/high risk transactions in the renewable energy sector. Many of these investments are first-in-kind market leaders in their respective countries and often involve FMO in a mandated lead arranger role.",
